---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Highway Fast Charging — Evium Charging"
  description="Turn your highway corridor location into a high-utilization EV charging destination. NEVI-compliant, no-cost deployments managed end-to-end by Evium."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center bg-evium-dark overflow-hidden pt-20">
    <!-- Background grid pattern -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(45,200,86,0.4) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(45,200,86,0.4) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"
    ></div>

    <!-- Radial glow -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[900px] h-[900px] rounded-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
      style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #2DC856 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Copy -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-evium-green/10 border border-evium-green/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-8">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-evium-green animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">NEVI-Ready Infrastructure</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-black text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6">
          Own the Corridor.<br />
          <span class="text-evium-green">Capture the Traffic.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-lg">
          Highway EV charging is a national infrastructure play — and Evium is your CPO. From NEVI grant applications to 24/7 uptime management, we handle everything. Zero cost to you. Revenue from day one.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact/quote"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-evium-green text-evium-dark font-bold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-evium-green/25"
          >
            Check NEVI Eligibility
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#opportunity"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-white/20 text-white/80 font-semibold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:border-evium-green/50 hover:text-white transition-all duration-200"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick stats -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 mt-12 pt-10 border-t border-white/10">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green">$0</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-1">Cost to Site Host</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white">$126K+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-1">Per Charger / 5 Years</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white">500+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-1">Chargers Installed</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Image -->
      <div class="relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-black/60 border border-white/10 max-w-lg w-full">
          <img
            src="/images/evium-dc-fast-outdoor-kiosk-combo.png"
            alt="Evium DC Fast Charging Outdoor Kiosk"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-evium-dark/60 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
            <div class="bg-evium-dark/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-3 border border-white/10">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div>
                  <div class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-0.5">DC Fast Charging</div>
                  <div class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Up to 300kW · NEVI Compliant</div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-evium-green animate-pulse"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative glow behind image -->
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-8 rounded-3xl opacity-20 pointer-events-none"
          style="background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #2DC856 0%, transparent 70%); z-index: -1;"
        ></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE HIGHWAY CHARGING OPPORTUNITY
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="opportunity" class="bg-evium-dark-light py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
        <div class="text-evium-green text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">The Opportunity</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Highway Charging Is the New Fuel Stop
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          EV adoption is accelerating faster than the charging network can scale. Highway corridors are the critical missing link — and site hosts who move now will define the landscape for the next decade.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green mb-3">40M+</div>
          <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">EVs on U.S. Roads by 2030</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every one of those drivers needs to charge on long-distance trips. Highway corridors become essential infrastructure, not optional amenities.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green mb-3">$7.5B</div>
          <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Federal NEVI Funding Allocated</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Congress has funded a national charging backbone along designated highway corridors. Sites that qualify can deploy at zero cost through Evium's CPO program.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green mb-3">First Mover</div>
          <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Advantage Is Real</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Sites that install now build brand recognition, driver loyalty, and dwell-time spend before competition arrives. The corridors are being claimed now.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green mb-3">15–45 min</div>
          <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Average Highway Dwell Time</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every charging session brings a captive customer into your store, restaurant, or amenity. EV drivers spend significantly more per stop than traditional fuel customers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green mb-3">180–300kW</div>
          <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Power That Matches Demand</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Highway drivers need fast charging — not slow trickle. Evium deploys 180kW to 300kW DC fast hardware that adds 100+ miles in under 20 minutes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green mb-3">100%</div>
          <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Managed by Evium</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Site hosts collect revenue without lifting a finger. Evium handles permitting, installation, software, compliance, maintenance, and uptime — start to finish.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       NEVI PROGRAM EXPLAINED
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/2 h-full opacity-5 pointer-events-none"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at right top, #2DC856 0%, transparent 60%);"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <!-- Left: Explainer -->
        <div>
          <div class="text-evium-green text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Federal Grant Program</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
            How NEVI Works — and Why Evium Is Your CPO
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            The National Electric Vehicle Infrastructure (NEVI) Formula Program distributes $7.5 billion in federal funding to build a national charging network. States issue grants to qualified Charging Point Operators (CPOs) to deploy hardware on designated Alternative Fuel Corridors (AFCs).
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Evium is a federally recognized CPO and has already secured NEVI site awards in New Mexico, grants from the California Energy Commission ($6MM+), and funding through the New Jersey BPU program. We've navigated every level of this bureaucracy — so you don't have to.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-evium-green/10 border border-evium-green/25 rounded-xl px-5 py-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-medium">Evium is a GSA-approved manufacturer partner and NEVI-compliant CPO. Your site is in qualified hands.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Step-by-step -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex items-center justify-center font-black text-evium-dark text-sm">1</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">Evium assesses your corridor location</div>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">We evaluate your site's AFC corridor status, utility access, traffic patterns, and grant eligibility in a single consult.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex items-center justify-center font-black text-evium-dark text-sm">2</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">We submit the NEVI application on your behalf</div>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">All federal, state, and utility paperwork is handled entirely by Evium. You sign where needed — nothing more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex items-center justify-center font-black text-evium-dark text-sm">3</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">Hardware is installed at no cost to you</div>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Grant funding covers the full cost of DC fast hardware, installation, and utility work. Zero capital expenditure for the site host.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex items-center justify-center font-black text-evium-dark text-sm">4</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">5-year contract + 5-year renewal option</div>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">You secure long-term infrastructure at your site with renewal rights, ensuring competitive advantage well into the decade.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex items-center justify-center font-black text-evium-dark text-sm">5</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">You earn a percentage of every charging session</div>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Site hosts receive a share of charging revenue. Evium handles billing, settlements, and compliance reporting — you receive a monthly payment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HARDWARE FOR HIGHWAY
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark-light py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <div class="text-evium-green text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">DC Fast Hardware</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Infrastructure-Grade Hardware for Every Corridor
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Highway charging demands more than a standard EV install. Every unit Evium deploys is a high-power DC fast charger built for continuous-duty, multi-vehicle throughput with NEVI compliance baked in.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Tellus 180kW -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/8 group hover:border-evium-green/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="relative bg-evium-dark h-64 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/tellus-dc-fast-180kw.png"
              alt="Tellus DC Fast 180kW"
              class="h-full w-full object-contain p-8 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
            />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-16 bg-gradient-to-t from-evium-dark to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-7">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Tellus Series</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-black mb-3">180kW DC Fast</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">The corridor workhorse. Dual CCS + CHAdeMO connectors, weatherproof outdoor enclosure, OCPP 1.6+ connectivity, and NEVI uptime compliance built in. Adds 100+ miles in under 20 minutes.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-evium-green/10 text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-evium-green/20">180kW Output</span>
              <span class="bg-white/5 text-white/60 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10">CCS + CHAdeMO</span>
              <span class="bg-white/5 text-white/60 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10">NEVI Compliant</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tellus 300kW -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-evium-green/25 group hover:border-evium-green/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-evium-green/10">
          <div class="relative bg-evium-dark h-64 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-evium-green text-evium-dark text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1 rounded-full z-10">Top Spec</div>
            <img
              src="/images/tellus-dc-fast-300kw.png"
              alt="Tellus DC Fast 300kW"
              class="h-full w-full object-contain p-8 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
            />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-16 bg-gradient-to-t from-evium-dark to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-7">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Tellus Series</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-black mb-3">300kW DC Fast</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Maximum throughput for high-traffic corridors. Supports dynamic power sharing across multiple vehicles simultaneously, ultra-fast 10-minute sessions for capable vehicles, and future-proof power delivery.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-evium-green/10 text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-evium-green/20">300kW Output</span>
              <span class="bg-white/5 text-white/60 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10">Dynamic Sharing</span>
              <span class="bg-white/5 text-white/60 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10">Future-Proof</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MaxiCharger -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/8 group hover:border-evium-green/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="relative bg-evium-dark h-64 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/maxicharger-dc-fast-60-240kw.png"
              alt="MaxiCharger DC Fast 60–240kW"
              class="h-full w-full object-contain p-8 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
            />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-16 bg-gradient-to-t from-evium-dark to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-7">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">MaxiCharger Series</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-black mb-3">60–240kW DC Fast</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Scalable modular architecture for sites with growing demand. Deploy at 60kW and upgrade to 240kW without replacing hardware. Ideal for sites entering the corridor market with room to scale.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-evium-green/10 text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-evium-green/20">60–240kW</span>
              <span class="bg-white/5 text-white/60 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10">Modular</span>
              <span class="bg-white/5 text-white/60 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10">Upgradeable</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-white/40 text-sm mt-10">Multi-stall configurations available. All hardware is GSA-approved and meets NEVI technical specifications. Evium handles equipment procurement, installation, and certification.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       REVENUE PROJECTIONS
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-1/2 h-full opacity-5 pointer-events-none"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at left bottom, #2DC856 0%, transparent 60%);"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <div class="text-evium-green text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Revenue Projections</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Passive Revenue From Day One
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Per a single 180kW NEVI-funded charger. Site hosts receive a percentage of charging revenue while Evium manages all operations. These are conservative estimates from our NEVI program proposals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <!-- Low utilization -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8 text-center">
          <div class="text-white/50 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Low Utilization</div>
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2">$900</div>
          <div class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-8">/ month per charger</div>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10 mb-8"></div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green mb-2">$54,000</div>
          <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Projected over 5 years</div>
          <p class="text-white/35 text-xs mt-6 leading-relaxed">Based on approximately 2–3 charging sessions per day at off-peak highway volumes.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Medium utilization — highlighted -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-evium-green/40 text-center relative shadow-xl shadow-evium-green/10">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-evium-green text-evium-dark text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">Typical Site</div>
          <div class="text-evium-green text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Medium Utilization</div>
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2">$1,500</div>
          <div class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-8">/ month per charger</div>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10 mb-8"></div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green mb-2">$90,000</div>
          <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Projected over 5 years</div>
          <p class="text-white/35 text-xs mt-6 leading-relaxed">Based on steady corridor traffic of 4–6 sessions per day at most U.S. highway sites.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- High utilization -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8 text-center">
          <div class="text-white/50 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">High Utilization</div>
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2">$2,100</div>
          <div class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-8">/ month per charger</div>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10 mb-8"></div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green mb-2">$126,000</div>
          <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Projected over 5 years</div>
          <p class="text-white/35 text-xs mt-6 leading-relaxed">Based on peak-corridor demand at major travel plazas, rest areas, and gas stations on high-volume routes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
